%% Diagram: DNS resolution flow (high-level)
%% Type: sequenceDiagram
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false, 'sequence': {'actorMargin': 12, 'messageMargin': 16, 'boxMargin': 5}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant Stub
    participant Rec
    participant Root
    participant TLD
    participant Auth

    Stub->>Rec: A?
    alt Cache hit
        Rec-->>Stub: Cached
    else Cache miss
        Rec->>Root: NS?
        Root-->>Rec: Refer .com
        Rec->>TLD: NS?
        TLD-->>Rec: Refer apex
        Rec->>Auth: A?
        Auth-->>Rec: A (TTL)
        Rec-->>Stub: Answer
    end
